      "content": "300mg a day?? isnt that kinda low for something meant to replace a prescription? i saw some people online saying you can take way more than that to actually feel the effects. also i'm already taking some ibuprofen for headaches, is it okay to keep taking those while switching over to the st johns wort? i don't want to have to go back to my doctor just to ask about a supplement.",
